                <p>There are many challenges to quick and easy data integrations, including:
                <ol>
                <li>Data comes from different sources, including internal IT systems (ERP, CRM, SCM), IoT devices, external data services (weather, foreign exchange, etc.)
                <li>Data is accessible in a wide variety of formats, including CSV files, REST Api, XML, YAML, MQTT
                <li>Access to data is often gated by IT departments making it slow and timing consuming for departments to get access to new integrated data.
                <li>Data needs to be stored in different formats and databases
                <li>Data needs to be visualized 
                </ol>
                </p>
